data.value:
Yet another Switch Lan Play GUI is a free to use GUI for LAN-Play Client.
Note that this is a "learning-by-doing"-Project which can contain errors/FEATURES! BTW: Yoshi helped us a lot!
YaSLP GUI uses the LANPlay-Client from spacemeowx2 (https://github.com/spacemeowx2/switch-lan-play).
YaSLP will get some Extra features like automatic Upgrade or language Files - but features like this will take some time as we mentioned above - we are still learning C#. We will do our best to implement new features as fast as possible.
KutaroKazuki & Batreaux
Project Page: https://github.com/batreaux-at/YaSLP-GUI
